{"tid":235173,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"(求救) 唔見身分證同學牌 後日考","createTime":"2017-05-08T19:45:31.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-14T20:44:41.000Z","uid":27161,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8928050a5d290f1ea167d3b1336d75e4ae5e910d","tid":235173,"uid":27161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T19:45:31.000Z","msg":"我今日(8/5)唔見銀包，入邊有身分證同學牌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但係後日考路試(11/5)，有無可能搞得切？<br />\n<br />\n上網睇考路試改期要七日前<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n跌銀包已經好傷，唔想準備左咁耐嘅路試要再報。。又要俾錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n跪求咁多位巴打幫手諗下有無辦法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n順手呻一句，連我同女朋友張即影即有都唔見埋。。真係好唔開心，好灰，補領樣樣都係錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19e5386ef5a128d53b944a7eab67e9a8bf2e82e4","tid":235173,"uid":6347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T19:47:29.000Z","msg":"學牌好似可以即比錢拎<br />\n聽日拎張行街紙衝去問下"},{"pid":"5c6dae9dd6b49cac53379d7999c335f220c6946a","tid":235173,"uid":22238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T19:48:34.000Z","msg":"應該搞得到<br />\n報失後再用臨時身份證申請學牌"},{"pid":"36678cb92866b7569025921e60f5d38ed05e4425","tid":235173,"uid":27161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T19:51:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>學牌好似可以即比錢拎<br />\n聽日拎張行街紙衝去問下</blockquote><br />\n行街紙係要去警署定入境處？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43d626af948e7113170fdb0486c222061116177b","tid":235173,"uid":27161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T19:52:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>應該搞得到<br />\n報失後再用臨時身份證申請學牌</blockquote><br />\n入境處最近都要10號先有位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"296ae650a2f511194db444ee76596b472d10aca1","tid":235173,"uid":51224,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T19:53:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>學牌好似可以即比錢拎<br />\n聽日拎張行街紙衝去問下</blockquote><br />\n行街紙係要去警署定入境處？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n入境處<br />\n最好開門前45分鐘去到排隊拎即日籌<br />\n去灣仔比較好<br />\n之後去金鐘運輸署問下行街紙考唔考得<br />\n考車當日除咗行街紙最好帶埋passport"},{"pid":"38019448fa5b2f6d695104f2411c0779607d18ac","tid":235173,"uid":47936,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T19:58:30.000Z","msg":"聽講考試唔洗學牌"},{"pid":"cff65186884a45f32d060e2469ee28b61601e06d","tid":235173,"uid":6347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T20:01:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>聽講考試唔洗學牌</blockquote><br />\n咁佢考之前都要操下車掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47b42a63a1c9032beb252e61b95d08a3d96614d5","tid":235173,"uid":27161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T20:10:10.000Z","msg":"我聽日就衝去搞張行街紙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n <br />\n唔該曬各位幫手，大恩大德 無以為報<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c66c602fa799a5efd6f49d8da50dd91ff60819d","tid":235173,"uid":51224,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T20:12:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我聽日就衝去搞張行街紙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n <br />\n唔該曬各位幫手，大恩大德 無以為報<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n祝事事順利<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb3f1b4872e472ef6